Package: ak
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, qt6-base-dev, libqt6widgets6
Recommends: gnupg
Description: Secure API Key Manager
 AK is a cross-platform command-line tool for managing API keys securely
 across different services. It provides encrypted storage, service integration,
 and comprehensive testing capabilities.
 .
 Key features:
  * Cross-platform support (Linux, macOS, Windows)
  * Secure encrypted storage with optional GPG encryption
  * Built-in support for popular APIs (OpenAI, GitHub, AWS, etc.)
  * Profile management for different environments
  * Shell completions for Bash, Zsh, and Fish
  * Comprehensive test suite with coverage reporting
  * Easy installation and configuration
